PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of Penelope Ann Denton, of Prince Rupert, British Columbia, as a director of the board of directors of the Prince Rupert Port Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective May 17, 1994, in the place of William B.M. Hick, whose term will expire.
